﻿@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,400,700" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: #1F2739;
            color: #A7A1AE;
        }

        .container {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #2C3446;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #4DC3FA;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #FB667A;
        }

        p, ul {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #A7A1AE;
        }

        a {
            color: #FB667A;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p>We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. In this policy, we explain how we collect, use, and store your data, as well as our limitations of liability.</p>

        <h2>Information Collection</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Personal data, such as your name, email address, phone number, and other information you provide when filling out forms.</li>
            <li>Automatically collected information, such as your IP address, browser and device data, access times, and the pages you visit on our website.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Use of Information</h2>
        <p>The collected data may be used for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Processing your requests and providing services.</li>
            <li>Improving our website and user experience.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Protection</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information; however, we cannot guarantee absolute security. We use standard security technologies, but please note that no method of transmitting data over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>We are not liable for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Unauthorized access to your information by third parties.</li>
            <li>Loss or damage of data as a result of using our website.</li>
            <li>Any losses or damages arising from the use of information obtained from our website.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Disclosure of Information</h2>
        <p>We do not disclose your personal information to third parties without your consent, except when required by law or to protect our rights.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Request access to your personal information.</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion of your information.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Changes to Our Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. All changes will be posted on our website with an effective date. We recommend periodically reviewing this page to stay informed of any changes.</p>

        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or comments regarding this policy or how we handle your data, please contact us.</p>
    </div>


    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>